Test plan
=========

* low level unit tests:
  - hkdf
  - account to username
  - etc.

* platform compliance unit tests (no server)
  - sha
  - aes
  - base32, base64
  - settings storage

* tests that involve server calls
  - resource
  - remote storage

* sync behaviour tests (require Sync server)
  - engine sync (syncStartup, processIncoming, uploadOutgoing, etc.)
  - service behaviour (meta/global, etc.)
  - end-to-end syncing
